Decoding Cravings It's important not to be too strict or to deny ourselves the foods we love or crave. The tension and emotional imbalances caused by suppression of cravings can accumulate and cause a regression to negative eating patterns. Cravings are a real need. They bring us emotional satisfaction, whichis calming anda delight to our senses. Diets should not be made so rigid. The elimination of harmful foods should be a comfortable, natural process which happens gradually. x2 as w | --> % 4  =
